name: Good Morning!
description: $GM is a culture coin that taps into the popular acronym "gm," which stands for "good morning" and is widely used on the X (formerly Twitter) timeline. By leveraging this common greeting, we aim to capture the mindshare of our community and foster a sense of connection and positivity. Our goal is to create a shared cultural experience where members can engage with one another daily, celebrating the simple yet meaningful act of starting the day with a cheerful "gm." Through $GM, we hope to build a vibrant and engaged community centered around positivity and shared moments.
